urdu transliteration text:
Kulsoom aur Ruqayya ke, haathon me rassiyan haiMasoom Sakina ke, hoton pe siskiyan hai,Badan zakhmi huwa muhari ka, aur garden mei tauq bhari hai
Innocent Sakina is sobbing,
@HujjatELC

Fizza ke peechay Zainab, khutbay sunaa rahi thiSayyedan ni o pe ummat, pathar gira rahi thiJurm kya tha, Ali ki beti ka, Iske sar se, rida utaari hay
Zainab was standing behind Fizza and giving sermons,
@HujjatELC
